com.interpss.simu.multicase
Interface MultiStudyCase

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Subinterfaces:
AclfMultiStudyCase, ContingencyAnalysis, DStabMultiStudyCase
All Known Implementing Classes:
AclfMultiStudyCaseImpl, ContingencyAnalysisImpl, DStabMultiStudyCaseImpl, MultiStudyCaseImpl
public interface MultiStudyCase
extends NameTag

A representation of the model object 'Multi Study Case'. Class for defining multiple study cases. LinkedList is used so that the studyCase could be used a queue

The following features are supported:

  • Net Type
  • Base Net Model String
  • Rule Base
  • Study Case List

See Also:
MulticasePackage.getMultiStudyCase()
